item.title: About
item.description: Korean version I’m a master’s student of the Department of Statistics at Chung-Ang University and I work in Multivariate Statistics Lab. My research interests are Functional Data Analysis(FDA), Spatio-temporal Data Analysis, Principal Component Analysis(PCA), Machine Learning, and I’m working on Functional principal component analysis(FPCA). I love R to handle the data, but I sometimes use Python. Education Master’s student in Statistics, Chung-Ang University, 2019.03 - Present B.A. in Applied Statistics,
